@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About us";
}
<div class="page-wrapper">
    <header class="page-heading clearfix">
        <h1 class="heading-title pull-left">About</h1>
        <div class="breadcrumbs pull-right">
            <ul class="breadcrumbs-list">
                <li class="breadcrumbs-label">You are here:</li>
                <li>@Html.ActionLink("Home", "index", "Home")<i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i></li>
                <li class="current">About</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <!--//breadcrumbs-->
    </header>
    <div class="page-content">
        <div class="row page-row">
            <article class="welcome col-md-8 col-sm-7">
                <h3 class="title">Welcome to Lahore Garrison University</h3>
                <p>
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="~/Content/images/750x300-about.jpg" alt="" /></p>
                <p>Establishment of Lahore Garrison University in The Punjab metropolis city of Lahore is an important milestone in the history of higher education in Pakistan.
                 In order to meet the global challenges it is necessary to touch the highest literacy rates while producing skillful and productive graduates in all fields of knowledge. Lahore Garrison University has been established to achieve the goal of excellence and quality education in minimum possible time.
                At present, LGU is running Undergraduate, Graduate, Masters, M. Phil and PhD programs in various disciplines. Main campus of LGU is located at the most developed area of Lahore, i.e Defense Phase-VI, Sector C, Avenue III which is easily approachable through Ring Road.
                 The campus, spreads on 65 kanals, comprises of multi-story academic blocks with spacious class rooms, well equipped labs, auditorium, library and cafeteria.
                </p>
                <ul class="custom-list-style">
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Serve the Society</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Producing skillful and productive Graduates</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Achieve the goal of excellence</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Promote the ethical, cultural and human values</li>
                </ul>

                <blockquote class="custom-quote">
                    <p><i class="fa fa-quote-left"></i>Highly qualified and experienced faculty has been hired to educate the students with latest developments in each discipline and enhance their creative abilities.</p>
                    <p class="people"><span class="name">Prof. Dr. Jamil Anwar</span><br>
                        <span class="title">Vice Chancellor</span></p>
                </blockquote>
                <p>
                    Jinnah Campus of LGU, which houses the intermediate. Boys & Girls Sections of  the University, is situated at 52-Tufail Road, near Flag Staff House crossing of Aziz Bhatti Road in the heart of Lahore Cantonment. Its central position makes it easy to access from all parts of the City.      
                </p>
            </article>
            <aside class="page-sidebar  col-md-3 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-1">
                @Html.Partial("~/Areas/FrontEnd/Views/Shared/Widgets/_Jobs.cshtml")
                @Html.Partial("~/Areas/FrontEnd/Views/Shared/Widgets/_EnquireAboutUs.cshtml")
            </aside>
        </div>
        <!--//page-row-->
    </div>
    <!--//page-content-->
</div><!--//page-->
